short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds FixUpX domain for easy embeds from X/Twitter

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
fuX, a project made to work alongside FixUpX, makes it easy to embed Twitter/X posts in places like Discord or Telegram. Instead of having to manually change a link from x.com to fixupx.com, it simply copies the already-formatted link with an easy to access button beneath the posts' media near the share and like buttons.

This is an open-source project that can be viewed, copied, altered, etc. on my GitHub:
https://github.com/TylerSDavies/fuX
